                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. PAYNE</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Hoe far had you to go from Kingsgate-street to your door? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> About ten yards.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350921-name-1189" type="witnessName">
