                  </hi>. I am a silversmith and jeweller. I have no<lb></lb>ticed Bray's ominbus going from Paddington to the Bank repeatedly—I have noticed other omnibuses near Mr. Bray's; in my opinion, they were racing against him—I have seen one behind him, and when Bray's omni<lb></lb>bus stopped, the other endeavoured to drive against him, in order to get his passengers—I should suppose if any timind female wanted to get into Bray's omnibus, she might have been alarmed by it; but I never saw that—I have seen one omnibus close before him as well as behind—when Bray's stopped, the others would stop—I have seen that—their conduct was such as to obstruct him in his regular course from Paddington to the Bank—I never saw any improper conduct of Bray's to the others.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
